---
title: Beef & Broccoli Stir-Fry with Udon Noodles & Roasted Peanuts
description: Spice up your night (and your tastebuds!) with this speedy stir-fry sensation that's sure to delight the whole family. Tender beef coated in a ginger-infused marinade is the star of the show, supported by an array of colourful veggies.
